29145709etSTGfqgsxHiZRBl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629145723mY8O3bowPxdAhENe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629145739QSN4hriTl18KzxjX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629145754BmY0LTPUEaqM9Gyb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629145823tpAxHVy7biW1BaLw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>郭培的首部艺术作品集《Couture Beyond》，由美国&nbsp;Rizzoli 出版社出版，纽约创意摄影团队&nbsp;HOWL Collective 制作。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143539j2KyChaLxuNGnHoY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.673594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143652Pact5B8CjZsuzLyk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.673594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143549orTYEf5HBJsN2bVx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.673594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806291435021TvkAlZKRzGXDHjp.png\" data-ratio=\"0.667897\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143516Z8cgCDWi05NYrzdV.png\" data-ratio=\"0.674074\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143523fW8pmyX9rKv20ZJV.png\" data-ratio=\"0.668299\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143533f6bhmj8IuV2GPsZR.png\" data-ratio=\"0.671166\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143601HABXLtP87UsxRjyK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.673594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143610kDHTer5xFhWtcSyf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.673594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143621LAcXzwhxYVIQo0Tu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.673594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143629klSx24X5PZVsf9Iq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.673594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143641OjAR7YSuoZc3QNtU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.673594\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143719Q8URMrTPEA71xCg4.png\" data-ratio=\"1.482759\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143726x9XMAObmwK0H1PS7.png\" data-ratio=\"0.633588\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><strong>大码超模&nbsp;Paloma Elsesser 和 Ashley Graham 登阿拉伯版《Vogue》最新封面。</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143801N5f1APQSVKHriLCW.png\" data-ratio=\"1.253612\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><strong>说唱歌手&nbsp;Kendrick Lamar 登《名利场》8 月封面。</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629143820EqN6hUzMiTmenfBk.png\" data-ratio=\"1.248387\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><strong>@larslala 是一个专门发布高跟鞋照片的账号。</strong>特别之处在于，所有照片中的鞋都看上去诡异而不合脚。背后的运营者是一位从事时尚自由撰稿的男性。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.dazeddigital.com/fashion/article/40498/1/instagram-of-the-week-larslala-ridiculous-fashion-shoes-catwak-fails\" rel=\"nofollow\">他在接受 dazed 采访时说</a>，这个账号存在的意义就是指出“高跟鞋的荒谬之处，尽管它让所有人看上去都更美丽。“</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629145952aqVhSIu0FtNcebAQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806291500383WtkgoXORdsLKClN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629145848ehpMNOKD0GwRmSuQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629145910sQjwlMIgehFS4Cn0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629145920ZrY72Qgxms9clk80.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629145928XYHGkUVTCBEIZ0mn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629145934bC0aSt7vT9euMYRm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629145943liMLQHTvztxpwNRn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806291459594mzSb3LqeQpOPakd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806291500077p3FaVPhJrkBwvqL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629150019KUs6bB7OMAcQNRCd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180629150027n03tNjAEJ4pgswhm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201806291500484Tei0wCBz7dOI5Q8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.194093\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图来自 <a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/rizzoli-otherwordly-creations-chinese-couture-visionary-guo-pei-monograph-howl-collective-06-28-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">郭培《Couture Beyond》</a></p>"}